local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["infelicitous"]={"infelicitous","[ɪnfɪ'lɪsɪtəs]","[ ,infi'lisitəs ]","adj.不幸的",'adj.不幸的,不吉的,不适当的','an infelicitous remark.','不恰当的评论','The infelicitous name makes sense when you break it down: Your thoughts and feelings (psycho) affect the chemicals in your brain (neuro), which affect the hormones that fight disease or replicate viruses (immunology).','当你把它分解后，这个不适当的名字（psychoneuroimmunology）就有意义了：你的思想和感情（心理psycho）影响你大脑的化学物质（神经neuro），从而影响与疾病或复制的病毒做斗争的激素（免疫学immuno）。'}
